value.string: The incoming object flow to a CallMBSEAnalyzer activity must match the type specified as the analysis case for the activity.
Binding connector must be connected to a parameter in at least one end.
A binding connector must be used to connect to a parameter. This connector will be ignored by MBSE Analyzer.
A constraint property must be named.
The AnalysisCase specified on the CallMBSEAnalyzerBehavior is invalid or malformed.
External analysis must have the URL tag defined.
